originalText.text: Solved my problem quickly when my bank refused to credit me with cash that I had deposited into their lobby ATM. Claim crossed 2 states, Vonnie knew the laws in both. Do not hesitate to use his reasonably priced services.

originalText.text:
I needed an attorney for a small claim case but didn’t have a lot of money, when I saw the price of  Mr. Vonnie Dones legal services fees I wasn’t sure if I want to use his service ( being so cheap)
However, from the time I hired Mr. Dones he was very professional, very polite, very knowledgeable and worked hard on my case. He kept me informed and gave me legal advice about my case. Mr. Dones went above and beyond to help me solve my small claim issues.
Nonetheless, I won my case and  got everything I sued for. I highly recommend Mr. Vonnie Dones legal services.
Thank you Mr.Dones

originalText.text: I had a case that was dismissed and an arrest record was still there. Confused and not sure what to do, I reached out to this company and Vonnie was excellent. Very helpful and responsive, explained why my record is still there (learned about 'expungement'). He knew the whole process and exactly what courts to talk to, exactly what to do. Afterwards he also helped me find services to remove the electronic records where they're not allowed. Thank you for your help Vonnie!
